%20largest%20investment%20groups.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Julia%20Kiryanova%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJulia%20Kiryanova%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Smart%20Holding%2C%20one%20of%20Ukraine's%20largest%20investment%20groups.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20is%20hoping%20governments%20and%20big%20firms%20will%20funnel%20billions%20of%20dollars%20to%20help%20Ukraine%20rebuild.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKiryanova%20helped%20with%20some%20government%20aid%20packages%2C%20but%20private%20investors%20remain%20hard%20to%20persuade.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Julia%20Kiryanova%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Smart%20Holding%2C%20one%20of%20Ukraine's%20largest%20investment%20groups.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20the%20CEO%20of%20Smart%20Holding%2C%20one%20of%20Ukraine's%20largest%20production%20and%20investment%20groups.%20I've%20been%20traveling%20to%20Western%20capitals%2C%20trying%20to%20get%20business%20leaders%20and%20policymakers%20to%20invest%20in%20my%20country's%20reconstruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20we've%20seen%20since%20the%20war%20started%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20governmental%20talk.%20Of%20course%2C%20there%20are%20lots%20of%20good%20reasons%20for%20that%20%E2%80%94%20military%20tasks%20are%20the%20prime%20ones%20for%20Ukraine%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that%20should%20not%20come%20at%20the%20price%20of%20a%20strong%20economy.%20And%20a%20strong%20economy%20is%20only%20possible%20when%20the%20corporate%20sector%20is%20an%20active%20participant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20the%20private%20sector%20and%20foreign%20investors%20can%20rebuild%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20am%20traveling%20to%20them%20so%20they%20can%20better%20understand%20Ukraine's%20needs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20I'm%20seeing%20policymakers%2C%20think%20tanks%2C%20business%20associations%2C%20and%20the%20businesses%20themselves%20in%20their%20own%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20them%20to%20understand%20the%20situation%20in%20Ukraine%20because%20sometimes%20they%20cannot%20get%20it%20through%20the%20media%20or%20through%20any%20other%20type%20of%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20also%20getting%20their%20views%2C%20their%20plans%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20how%20we%20can%20support%20each%20other%20in%20assisting%20this%20process%20and%20building%20partnerships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20been%20discussing%20with%20officials%20at%20the%20State%20Department%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20how%20we%20can%20improve%20communications%20between%20the%20private%20and%20public%20sectors%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Julia%20Kiryanova%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Capitol%20Building%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6582d842a79e5746976b6ba1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulia%20Kiryanova%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Capitol%20Building%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20where%20she%20spoke%20with%20State%20Department%20officials.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Julia%20Kiryanova%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20I%20discussed%20Ukraine's%20reconstruction%20with%207%20or%208%20MPs%20of%20the%20UK%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20two%20very%20productive%20meetings%20with%20the%20European%20Commission%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20its%20Ukraine%20Facility%20proposing%20to%20provide%20%2454%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20discussed%20practical%20matters%2C%20like%20how%20to%20finance%20that%20facility%20in%20line%20with%20international%20financial%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Editor's%20note%3A%20Since%20Kiryanova%20spoke%20to%20BI%2C%20the%20EU%20spending%20package%20was%20blocked.%20Hungary%2C%20one%20of%20the%2027%20member%20states%2C%20vetoed%20the%20plan.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Germany%2C%20I%20met%20with%20advisors%20to%20the%20Chancellery%20as%20well%20as%20MPs%20from%20the%20Bundestag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Julia%20Kiryanova%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6582ee22cefc010bea256bff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulia%20Kiryanova%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20in%20London%2C%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20outside%20the%20European%20Parliament%20building%20in%20Brussels%2C%20Belgium%2C%20and%20inside%20the%20German%20Parliament%20in%20Berlin%2C%20Germany.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Julia%20Kiryanova%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20those%20talks%2C%20I%20tell%20them%20there%20are%20business%20opportunities%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20value%20they%20can%20get%20out%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20am%20laying%20the%20ground%20work%20and%20building%20momentum%20for%20the%20post-war%20economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20I%20have%20not%20heard%20any%20promises%20of%20investments%20in%20Ukraine's%20industry%20from%20private%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20am%20focused%20on%20the%20long%20run.%20I%20do%20not%20hope%20someone%20will%20invest%20immediately%20tomorrow.%20If%20I%20had%20these%20hopes%2C%20I'd%20be%20frustrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20now%20working%20on%20long-term%20relationships%2C%20which%20need%20time%20and%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20foreign%20investors%20could%20adjust%20their%20risk%20appetite%2C%20they%20could%20invest%20with%20us%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20I'm%20saying%20%E2%80%94%20now%20is%20the%20time%20to%20invest.%20And%20those%20who%20take%20this%20risk%20today%20will%20reap%20the%20benefits%20afterwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20need%20to%20take%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMassive%20investment%20will%20come%20after%20the%20war%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20me%2C%20Ukraine's%20reconstruction%20goes%20through%20two%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20phase%20is%20when%20there%20will%20be%20government-to-government%20assistance%20to%20rebuild%20some%20of%20the%20key%20infrastructure%20and%20key%20housing%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20a%20clear%20responsibility%20of%20the%20state%20because%20only%20governments%20can%20generate%20the%20capital%20required%20for%20such%20reconstruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20second%20phase%20is%20when%20the%20private%20sector%20comes%20into%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20that%20time%2C%20the%20investment%20climate%20and%20the%20incentives%20should%20be%20there%20for%20a%20boost%20in%20Ukraine's%20economy.%20The%20boost%20will%20only%20come%20when%20the%20private%20investors%20have%20a%20clear%20vision%20of%20how%20they%20can%20get%20their%20money%20into%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I'm%20not%20saying%20the%20private%20sector%20will%20not%20invest%20during%20the%20first%20phase%20or%20even%20during%20the%20war.%20I'm%20saying%20%3Cem%3Emassive%3C%2Fem%3E%20investment%20will%20only%20come%20after%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20private%20sector%20to%20get%20prepared%20to%20invest%20at%20that%20second%20stage%2C%20we%20need%20to%20have%20all%20these%20discussions%20now.%20Foreign%20investors%20need%20to%20get%20to%20know%20the%20market%2C%20the%20local%20partners%2C%20and%20the%20pre-conditions%20for%20investment.%20This%20is%20all%20now%20%E2%80%94%20not%20after%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20is%20hard%20work%20but%20I%20am%20a%20realist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20realistic%20about%20the%20challenges%20ahead.%20Ukraine%20is%20in%20a%20very%20difficult%20situation%20with%20an%20unknown%20time%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20the%20messaging%20can%20be%20frustrating%2C%20especially%20with%20aid%20packages%20not%20being%20approved%20by%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20critical%20%E2%80%94%20or%20the%20EU.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20do%20believe%20we're%20having%20success.%20We've%20held%20conferences%20about%20Ukraine's%20reconstruction%20in%20Lugano%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20and%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20we're%20holding%20one%20in%20Berlin%2C%20Germany%2C%20in%20June%20%E2%80%94%20Ukraine's%20third-biggest%20conference%20on%20reconstruction.%20These%20conferences%20are%20milestones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20private%20sector%20is%20there%2C%20then%20it%20is%20a%20success.%20Again%2C%20there%20is%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-lobby-for-international-investment-in-ukraine-reconstruction-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703752681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658048e4a79e5746976a695f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-lobby-for-international-investment-in-ukraine-reconstruction-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Julia%20Kiryanova%20traveled%20to%20Berlin%2C%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20Brussels%2C%20and%20London%20to%20lobby%20business%20leaders%20and%20lawmakers%20to%20invest%20in%20Ukraine's%20reconstruction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-lobby-for-international-investment-in-ukraine-reconstruction-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221st%20Test%2C%20Day%203%20Live%3A%20Dean%20Elgar%20Hits%20150%20As%205-Down%20SA%20Cruise%20vs%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIND%20vs%20SA%20Live%20Score%2C%201st%20Test%2C%20Day%203%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%C2%A0India's%20search%20for%20a%20wicket%20goes%20on%20with%20Dean%20Elgar%20and%20Marco%20Jansen%20going%20strongly%20after%20the%20start%20of%20play%20on%20Day%203.%20The%20hosts%20were%20256%2F5%20before%20bad%20lig