sian-soldiers-execute-surrendered-ukrainian-troops-probe-launched-4756819%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSita%20Mata%20Has%20Withdrawn%20Her%20Curse%26quot%3B%3A%20'King'%20Of%20Ayodhya%20On%20City%20Revamp%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20has%20received%20over%20100%20applications%20for%20permission%20to%20build%20five-star%20hotels%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20which%20did%20not%20have%20a%20proper%20hotel%20even%20a%20few%20years%20back%2C%20the%20man%20widely%20known%20as%20'King%20of%20Ayodhya'%20told%20NDTV%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20grand%20consecration%20event%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBimlendra%20Mohan%20Pratap%20Mishra%20is%20a%20member%20of%20Ayodhya%20royal%20family%20that%20goes%20back%20to%20King%20Darshan%20Singh%2C%20believed%20to%20have%20ruled%20the%20kingdom%20sometime%20in%20the%2019th%20century.%20Referred%20to%20as%20Raja%20Saheb%20in%20the%20city%2C%20he%20has%20been%20involved%20with%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20since%20it%20began.%20He%20is%20also%20a%20member%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%2C%20which%20is%20overseeing%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%20after%20Supreme%20Court's%20landmark%20verdict%20in%20the%20land%20dispute%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEver%20since%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%2C%20there%20is%20an%20environment%20of%20joy%20(in%20Ayodhya).%20The%20temporary%20temple%20was%20built.%20On%20holidays%2C%20Tuesdays%2C%20any%20festival%2C%20there%20is%20no%20space%20to%20even%20walk.%20Ayodhya%20did%20not%20have%20a%20proper%20hotel%2C%20and%20now%20more%20than%20100%20applications%20to%20open%20five-star%20hotels%20have%20come%20in%2C%20the%20district%20magistrate%20told%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyodhya%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20also%20being%20developed%20as%20a%20Smart%20City.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20in%20five%20years%2C%20people%20will%20come%20not%20just%20for%20darshan%2C%20but%20to%20see%20the%20city.%20Ayodhya%20will%20be%20known%20as%20the%20best%20holy%20town%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mishra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyodhya%20is%20undergoing%20a%20massive%20revamp%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20grand%20event%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20city%20is%20getting%20a%20new%20airport%20and%20its%20railway%20station%20is%20being%20given%20a%20new%20look%20and%20facilities%20that%20will%20help%20crores%20of%20pilgrims%20visiting%20the%20holy%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20all-round%20development%2C%20Mr%20Mishra%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20appears%20that%20Mata%20Sita%20has%20withdrawn%20her%20curse%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyodhya%2C%20according%20to%20local%20legend%2C%20had%20been%20cursed%20by%20Sita%20when%20she%20was%20banished%20from%20the%20city%20by%20Lord%20Ram%20over%20rumours.%20It%20is%20owing%20to%20the%20curse%20that%20the%20city%20never%20saw%20speedy%20development%2C%20many%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mishra's%20association%20with%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20goes%20back%20more%20than%20three%20decades.%20In%201990%2C%20when%20at%20least%2050%20karsevaks%20were%20killed%20in%20police%20firing%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20he%20had%20sheltered%20many%20karsevaks%20at%20his%20palace%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20never%20hoped%20that%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20see%20Ram%20Mandir's%20construction%20in%20my%20lifetime.%20It%20is%20my%20good%20fortune%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703750640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fa37rb30o_ayodhya-development-pti_625x300_28_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-ram-temple-inauguration-sita-mata-has-withdrawn-her-curse-king-of-ayodhya-on-development-wave-4756513%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20administration%20has%20received%20over%20100%20applications%20for%20permission%20to%20build%20five-star%20hotel