If%20it%20is%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20good%20thing.%20But%20I%20doubt%20it%2C%20since%20the%20whole%20intention%20is%20to%20have%20a%20saffronised%20Pakistan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Giriraj%20Pai%20Vernekar%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Goa%20BJP%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fformer-mumbai-top-cop-comments-minorities-bjp-fire-goa-9085409%2F%5C%22%3E%20criticised%20Ribeiro%E2%80%99s%20comparisons%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20describing%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunfounded%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20offensive%20to%20the%20ethos%20and%20achievements%20of%20our%20great%20nation.%E2%80%9D%20Vernekar%20accused%20Ribeiro%20of%20harbouring%20%E2%80%9Cdeep%20hatred%20and%20frustration%20at%20having%20a%20government%20in%20power%20that%20possibly%20does%20not%20conform%20to%20his%20ideology.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20to%20demean%20the%20country%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20belittle%20the%20government%20is%20unbecoming%20of%20a%20former%20cop.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERibeiro%20was%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20Mumbai%20Police%20from%201982%20to%201986%20and%20later%20held%20the%20post%20of%20Director%20General%20of%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20and%20then%20Director%20General%20Police%20of%20Gujarat.%20He%20also%20served%20as%20Indian%20Ambassador%20to%20Romania%20from%201989%20until%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703747349000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F28123436%2FCopy-of-