ed-thousands-on-trespassing-charges-at-the-border-illegal-crossings-are-still-high%2Famp_articleshow%2F106343248.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22COMIC%3A%20I%20survived%20the%20capsizing%20of%20the%20Adriana%2C%20which%20sank%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Greece%20while%20the%20world%20was%20transfixed%20on%20the%20Titan%20sub%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Adriana%20thumb%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658cc3451c5c7b8c9a0c6d60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJosh%20Adams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20the%20world's%20attention%20was%20rapt%2C%20as%20a%20submersible%20that%20escorted%20wealthy%20customers%20to%20see%20the%20sunken%20%3Cem%3ETitanic%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0disappeared%20with%20five%20souls%20on%20board.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Mediterranean%2C%20a%20different%20horror%20was%20unfolding%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fishing%20trawler%20converted%20to%20transport%20migrants%20out%20of%20Libya%20capsized%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Greece%2C%20claiming%20hundreds%20of%20lives%20in%20one%20of%20the%20deadliest%20recent%20incidents%20in%20the%20unfolding%20humanitarian%20disaster%20in%20the%20Mediterranean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fem%3E%20interviewed%C2%A0survivors%20of%20the%20sinking%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EAdriana%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20after%20several%20interviews%20adapted%20the%20experiences%2C%20photographs%2C%20and%20testimony%20of%20one%20man%2C%20a%20Syrian%20immigrant%20named%20Mohammad%20Lheman%2C%20into%20this%20comic.%20It%20takes%20you%20where%20news%20cameras%20cannot%20go%2C%20into%20the%20sprawling%20underground%20world%20of%20smugglers%2C%20the%20reckless%20treatment%20of%20human%20life%2C%20and%20through%20a%20harrowing%20ordeal%20in%20the%20waters%20of%20the%20Mediterranean%20that%20most%20did%20not%20survive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%20name%20is%20Mohammad%20Lheman.%20I%20was%20born%20in%20Palestine%20but%20raised%20in%20Syria.%20When%20I%20was%20four%20and%20five%20years%20old%20we%20would%20go%20to%20the%20swimming%20pool%20in%20the%20summer%20all%20the%20time.%20It%20was%20a%20joyful%20thing.%20My%20father%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20swim.%20It%20was%20magnificent.%20I%20loved%20being%20in%20the%20water%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658d0cb5ab6f2ebb11f74a7b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226642%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3E%EF%B9%92%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%222022.%20Damascus%2C%20Syria.%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20barber%20in%20a%20luxury%20salon.%20I%20enjoyed%20it%20but%20the%20hours%20killed%20me.%20I%20worked%20fourteen%20hours%20a%20day.%20I%20had%20Mondays%20off%20and%20took%20agricultural%20engineering%20classes%20at%20university.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20my%20favorite%20subject%20but%20because%20I%20was%20working%20most%20of%20the%20time%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20the%20marks%20I%20needed%20for%20other%20programs.%20The%20quality%20of%20life%20was%20horrible.%20Often%20no%20water.%20No%20electricity.%20I%20had%20an%20obligation%20to%20join%20the%20army%2C%20but%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to.%20My%20younger%20cousin%20Hamza%20and%20I%20would%20see%20each%20other%20at%20night.%20He%20was%20a%20lifeguard%20at%20the%20local%20pool.%20Sometimes%20my%20older%20cousin%20Abdulrahman%20would%20join%20us.%20%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20join%20the%20army%20either.%20So%20we%20decided%20we%20wanted%20to%20get%20out.%20Go%20to%20Europe.%20I%20had%20a%20cousin%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20and%20decided%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20I%20would%20go.%20My%20father%20sold%20the%20upstairs%20of%20the%20house%20to%20get%20us%20out.%20We%20found%20a%20smuggler%20in%20Libya%20who%20would%20help%20us%20get%20to%20Europe%20through%20Italy.%20I%20paid%20%241%2C500.%20It%20was%20glorious%20to%20leave%20Syria.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658d0cb5ab6f2ebb11f74a77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225602%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3E%EF%B9%92%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22We%20arrived%20in%20Libya.%20Paid%20a%20man%20to%20get%20us%20to%20our%20smuggler.%20A%20taxi%20cab%20drove%20us%20to%20the%20smuggler.%20We%20paid%20him.%20Most%20smugglers%20are%20Syrians%20working%20in%20Libya%20under%20other%20smugglers.%20The%20smuggler%20drove%20us%20for%20six%20hours%20to%20his%20home.%20Nineteen%20of%20us%20stayed%20in%20his%20basement.%20And%20then%20they%20moved%20us%20to%20another%20house.%20And%20another%20house.%20And%20another.%20And%20another.%20One%20day%20we%20were%20taken%20to%20the%20desert%20and%20lost.%20%20We%20were%20told%20we%20had%20to%20pay%20%2410%20to%20get%20us%20back.%20They%20told%20us%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20to%20leave%20the%20house.%20We%20would%20be%20threatened%20every%20day.%20Told%20they%20would%20burn%20the%20house%20and%20keep%20us%20in%20there.%20It%20was%20sixty%20days%20of%20this.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658d0cb51c5c7b8c9a0c7061%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%228594%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3E%EF%B9%92%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22June%2010%2C%202023.%201%3A00am.%20They%20took%20me%20from%20the%20house%20to%20the%20coast.%20I%20asked%20the%20smuggler%20to%20buy%20me%20some%20nausea%20medicine.%20Paid%20him%20%2420.%20It%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work.%20I%20vomited%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20was%20in%20the%20small%20boat.%20The%20boat%20looked%20old.%20The%20wood%20was%20rotten.%20It%20was%20damaged.%20The%20boat%20had%20a%20capacity%20of%20300%20people.%20%20They%20stuffed%20747%20people%20on%20this%20boat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658d0cb31c5c7b8c9a0c705b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224042%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3E%EF%B9%92%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20boat%20was%20three%20levels.%20The%20standard%20level%20was%20where%20you%20boarded.%20A%20hole%20would%20take%20you%20down%20the%20bottom%20level.%20A%20freezer.%20It%E2%80%99s%20where%20the%20fish%20would%20be%20stored.%20It%20smelled%20badly.%20I%20vomited%20on%20my%20way%20down%20and%20I%20refused%20to%20go%20down.%20They%20wanted%20to%20hit%20me%20and%20punch%20me%20to%20go%20down.%20I%20paid%20them%20%2440.%20They%20took%20me%20upstairs.%20We%20were%20the%20first%20people%20to%20get%20there.%20Upper%20deck%3A%20Approximately%20two%20hundred%20and%20fifty%20people.%20All%20paid%20extra%20to%20be%20up%20there.%20Mainly%20Syrians%20and%20Egyptians.%20Middle%20deck.%20Two%20hundred%20people.%20Women%20and%20children.%20Bottom%20level.%20Two%20hundred%20people.%20Mainly%20Pakistanis%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658d16e2ec62ab5daf7f2308%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3E%EF%B9%92%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22June%2010%20and%2011%20Day%20One%20and%20Day%20Two.%20I%20had%20brought%20some%20food%20and%20water%20in%20my%20bag%20but%20the%20smugglers%20took%20it%20away%20from%20me%20before%20I%20boarded.%20Said%20they%20needed%20the%20extra%20room.%20During%20the%20day%20it%20was%20hot.%20The%20sun%20would%20beat%20down%20on%20us.%20At%20night%20it%20was%20freezing.%20My%20cousin%20Hamza%20was%20only%20a%20meter%20away%20from%20me.%20He%20was%20getting%20weak.%20My%20cousin%20Abdulrahman%20was%20also%20by%20me.%20I%20snuck%20in%20a%20Snickers%20bar%20in%20my%20pocket.%20I%20tried%20not%20to%20eat%20it.%20To%20save%20it.%20But%20after%20two%20days%20I%20needed%20to%20eat%20something.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658d0cb3ab6f2ebb11f74a70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224428%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3E%EF%B9%92%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22June%2012%20and%2013.%20Day%20Three%20and%20Day%20Four.%20On%20the%20third%20day%20there%20was%20no%20more%20water.%20People%20were%20so%20desperate%20they%20started%20to%20drink%20unfiltered%20engine%20water.%20Really%20dirty%20stuff.%20Some%20were%20drinking%20urine.%20We%20could%20hear%20the%20moaning%20and%20suffering%20below%20us.%20Help%20us!%20We%20need%20water!%20We%E2%80%99re%20dying!%20My%20child%20is%20dying!!%20People%20started%20fainting.%20Passing%20out.%20People%20starting%20fighting.%20We%20realized%20we%20were%20completely%20lost.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658d0cb41c5c7b8c9a0c705c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225780%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3E%EF%B9%92%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22June%2014.%20Day%20Five.%20One%20of%20the%20Syrian%20men%20took%20his%20satellite%20phone%20and%20started%20calling.%20Reached%20out%20to%20Doctors%20without%20Borders.%20Or%20the%20Navy%20or%20the%20Coast%20Guard%20of%20any%20country.%20He%20sent%20our%20location%20to%20them.%20They%20told%20us%20we%20were%20in%20Greek%20waters%2C%20not%20Italian.%20At%20around%2012%20o%E2%80%99clock%20a%20helicopter%20flew%20above%20us%2C%20taking%20pictures%20and%20videos.%20And%20then%20a%20few%20hours%20later%20a%20commercial%20ship%20going%20slowly%20was%20near%20us.%20We%20all%20got%20to%20our%20feet%20and%20waved%20our%20clothes.%20Yelled%20to%20it.%20Help%20us!%20Over%20here!%20Please!%20%20The%20boat%20called%20Faithful%20Warrior%20came%20by%20and%20threw%20us%20water%20and%20food%20on%20a%20rope.%20It%20was%20only%20enough%20for%20twenty%20people.%20It%20left.%20Another%20commercial%20ship%20called%20Lucky%20Strike%20came%20by%20a%20couple%20hours%20later.%20They%20also%20threw%20food%20and%20water.%20We%20yelled%20at%20them%20asking%20for%20them%20to%20take%20us%20with%20them.%20Our%20boat%20started%20to%20shake.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20our%20ship%E2%80%99s%20captain%20put%20the%20engine%20on%20the%20left%20to%20get%20away%20from%20the%20ship.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658d0cb41c5c7b8c9a0c705e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%227404%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3E%EF%B9%92%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22June%2014.%20Eleven%20o%E2%80%99clock%20pm.%20The%20Greek%20Coast%20Guard%20ship%20came%20at%20night.%20It%20was%20truly%2C%20truly%20huge.%20They%20sent%20over%20a%20rope%20and%20it%20was%20tied%20to%20the%20front%20of%20our%20boat.%20It%20was%20tied%20very%2C%20very%20badly.%20The%20Coast%20Guard%20ship%20then%20started%20pulling%20us%20very%20quickly.%20Too%20quickly.%20It%20moved%20to%20the%20left%20and%20our%20entire%20boat%20lost%20its%20balance%20and%20tilted%20to%20the%20left.%20People%20started%20yelling%20at%20them.%20Stop!%20Stop!%20Stop!%20%20The%20Coast%20Guard%20ship%20stopped.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658d0cb3ab6f2ebb11f74a6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224233%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3E%EF%B9%92%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22But%20then%20five%20seconds%20later%20the%20Coast%20Guard%20Ship%20started%20again.%20Our%20boat%20started%20to%20tip%20over.%20And%20thirty%20seconds%20later%20flipped%20