ata%20who%20founded%20the%20Tata%20Group.%20He%20was%20born%20on%20December%2028%2C%201937%2C%20in%20Mumbai%20to%20Naval%20Tata%20and%20Sooni%20Tata.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20was%20raised%20by%20his%20grandmother%2C%20Navajbai%20Tata%20after%20his%20parents%20separated%20in%201948.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDespite%20coming%20close%20to%20marriage%20on%20four%20occasions%2C%20Ratan%20Tata%20is%20still%20unmarried.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20once%20admitted%20that%20he%20fell%20in%20love%20while%20working%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20But%20because%20of%20the%20ongoing%201962%20Indo-China%20War%2C%20the%20girl's%20parents%20refused%20to%20let%20her%20move%20to%20India.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECommencing%20his%20career%20in%201961%2C%20Ratan%20Tata%20started%20from%20the%20ground%20up%2C%20managing%20operations%20on%20the%20shop%20floor%20of%20Tata%20Steel.%20This%20experience%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20his%20future%20leadership%20role%20within%20the%20group.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20began%20restructuring%20the%20Tata%20group%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20liberalisation%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy%20was%20underway.%20He%20played%20an%20instrumental%20role%20in%20the%20business%20expansion%20of%20popular%20cars%20including%20the%20Tata%20Nano%20and%20Tata%20Indica.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20got%20Tata%20Tea%20to%20acquire%20Tetley%2C%20Tata%20Motors%20to%20acquire%20Jaguar%20Land%20Rover%2C%20and%20Tata%20Steel%20to%20acquire%20Corus%20in%202004.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%202009%2C%20Ratan%20fulfilled%20his%20promise%20to%20make%20the%20world's%20cheapest%20car%20accessible%20to%20the%20middle%20class.%20The%20Tata%20Nano%2C%20priced%20at%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%20became%20a%20symbol%20of%20innovation%20and%20affordability.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWith%20over%2012%20million%20followers%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Ratan%20Tata%20is%20the%20'most%20followed%20entrepreneur'%20in%20the%20country%2C%20according%20to%20the%20360%20ONE%20Wealth%20Hurun%20India%20Rich%20Li