%2Fphotostory%2F106302203.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Cricket%20Is%20Being%20Dominated%20By...'%3A%20SA%20Legend%20Makes%20Explosive%20Statement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20instrumental%20in%20exposing%20BCCI%20to%20the%20whole%20new%20world%20of%20commercialisation%20of%20the%20game's%20broadcast%20but%20former%20Cricket%20South%20Africa%20president%20Dr%20Ali%20Bacher%20doesn't%20like%20only%20three%20boards%20%26quot%3Bmarginalising%26quot%3B%20others%20in%20order%20to%20enjoy%20complete%20hegemony.%20It%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20India%2C%20Australia%20and%20England%20cricket%20boards%20decide%20the%20cricket%20calendar%20and%20Bacher%2C%20who%20brought%20the%20Proteas%20cricket%20to%20mainstream%2C%20post-apartheid%2C%20isn't%20amused%20at%20all.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20the%20chairman%20of%20ICC's%20development%20committee%2C%20my%20objective%20was%20to%20spread%20the%20game.%20It's%20not%20happening%20today.%20Cricket%20today%20is%20dominated%20by%20India%2C%20Australia%2C%20England.%20South%20Africa%20has%20been%20marginalised%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20marginalised%2C%20West%20Indies%20has%20been%20marginalised.%20That's%20not%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20Bacher%2C%20now%2081%2C%20told%20PTI%20during%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20while%20watching%20the%20India%20and%20South%20Africa%20opening%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20grow%20the%20game.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20finance%20of%20world%20cricket%20is%20dominated%20by%20India%20and%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20world%20cricket%20money%20comes%20through%20India%20from%20whatever%20direction.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20see%20development%20of%20smaller%20nations%2C%20that%20was%20my%20profound%20passion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDevelopment%20of%20cricket%20in%20US%20is%20not%20viable%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20is%20aiming%20to%20promote%20cricket%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20first%20few%20steps%20include%2C%20awarding%20co-hosting%20rights%20for%20next%20year's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20and%20also%20inclusion%20of%20cricket%20in%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Olympics%20in%202028%20as%20a%20part%20of%20one%20of%20the%20games%20inducted%20by%20Local%20Organising%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20astute%20administrator%2C%20the%20former%20South%20African%20Test%20captain%20(pre-apartheid%20era)%2C%20however%2C%20isnt%20too%20hopeful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it%20will%20grow%20massively%20as%20you%20expect%20it%20to%20grow%20in%20USA.%20I%20was%20keen%20on%20spreading%20cricket%20as%20chairman%20of%20ICC%20Development%20Committee%2C%20to%20get%20into%20USA.%20Oh%2C%20its%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recollected.%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20billions%20and%20billions%20of%20dollars%20to%20get%20a%20small%20niche%20of%20that%20(USA)%20market.%20To%20be%20honest%2C%20I%20called%20it%20a%20day%20after%20two%20occasions.%20It%20wasn't%20going%20to%20happen.%20The%20way%20it%20should%20happen%20is%2C%20growth%20of%20cricket%20should%20be%20in%20Asia.%20There%20is%20enormous%20potential.%20Not%20in%20the%20USA%20as%20its%20far%20too%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20reasoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20why%20it%20is%20not%20commercially%20viable%2C%20he%20further%20explained%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20amount%20of%20money%20they%20spent%20on%20baseball%2C%20basketball%20and%20rugby%20is%20massive.%20To%20get%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20that%20market%20costs%20billion%20dollars%20and%20it%20would%20take%20time.%20Lot%20easier%20to%20get%20cricket%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSouth%20Korea%2C%20Japan%20are%20huge%20markets%20potentially.%20If%20those%20countries%20take%20to%20baseball%2C%20why%20won't%20they%20take%20to%20cricket%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20close%20touch%20with%20UK%20and%20English%20empire.%20But%20don't%20even%20try%20going%20to%20US%2C%20you%20will%20come%20short%2C%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20a%20sort%20warning%20for%20ICC%20bigwigs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalk%20about%20South%20African%20cricket%2C%20Bacher%20admits%20that%20the%20national%20team%20lacks%20world%20class%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20so%20strong%20as%20we%20used%20to%20be%2C%20we%20had%20unbelievable%20players%20earlier%2C%20AB%20de%20Villiers%2C%20Jacques%20Kallis%20and%20Shaun%20Pollock%2C%20we%20now%20have%20Kagiso%20(Rabada)%20who%20is%20world%20class%20and%20we%20have%20gone%20through%20a%20period%20where%20quality%20of%20our%20top%20cricketers%20isn't%20what%20it%20used%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20very%20good%20schools%20cricket%20and%20we%20will%20come%20back%20and%20remain%20a%20strong%20a%20side.%26quot%3B%20In%201991%2C%20when%20South%20Africa%2C%20after%20the%20end%20of%20apartheid%20period%2C%20travelled%20to%20India%20for%20its%20first%20three-match%20ODI%20series%2C%20the%20BCCI%20for%20the%20first%20time%20received%201.25%20million%20rands%20(around%20120%2C000%20USD%20at%20that%20time)%20as%20broadcast%20rights%20money%20to%20air%20the%20games%20back%20in%20the%20'Rainbow%20Nation'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20asked%20(Jagmohan)%20Dalmiya%2C%20how%20much%20people%20would%20come%20to%20watch%2C%20he%20said%20around%20100%2C000%20at%20Eden%20Gardens.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20cricket%20broadcast%20in%20India%20was%20controlled%20by%20Doordarshan.%20I%20offered%20a%20quarter%20million%20rands%20and%20he%20(Dalmiya)%20he%20couldn't%20believe%20it.%26quot%3B%20So%20is%20he%20surprised%20at%20India's%20commercial%20growth%20and%20he%20answers%20in%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20really%2C%20because%20there%20are%201.4%20billion%20people%20in%20South%20Africa%20and%20they%20are%20mad%20about%20cricket%2C%20commercial%20value%20of%20cricket%20is%20huge%20and%20if%20I%20was%20in%20a%20small%20way%20party%20to%20it%2C%20I%20was%20very%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703744520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fop53e9d8_sdad_625x300_28_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fcricket-is-being-dominated-by-south-africa-legend-makes-explosive-statement-4752824%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Cricket%20South%20Africa%20president%20Dr%20Ali%20Bacher%20was%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20dominance%20of%20certain%20cricket%20boards%20in%20the%20current%20game.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fcricket-is-being-dominated-by-south-africa-legend-makes-explosive-statement-4752824%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fcricket-is-being-dominated-by-south-africa-legend-makes-explosive-statement-4752824%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fcricket-is-being-dominated-by-south-africa-legend-makes-explosive-statement-4752824%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suzlon%20bags%20300%20MW%20project%20from%20Apraava%20Energy%20to%20supply%20wind%20turbines%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703744409000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-02%2F28%2Ffull%2F1582906239-5779.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsuzlon-bags-300-mw-project-from-apraava-energy-to-supply-wind-turbines-123122800236_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Suzlon%20will%20instal%20100%20Wind%20Turbine%20Generators%20(WTGs)%20with%20a%20Hybrid%20Lattice%20Tubular%20(HLT)%20tower%2C%20and%20a%20rated%20capacity%20of%203%20MW%20each%20at%20the%20client's%20site%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20a%20company%20statement%20said%22%2C