0his%20name%20and%20added%20'kanth'.%20As%20for%20the%20title%20'Captain'%2C%20it%20came%20from%20his%20character%20in%201991%20movie%20Captain%20Prabhakaran%2C%20in%20which%20he%20played%20a%20forest%20officer.%20In%201990%2C%20he%20married%20Premalatha%2C%20who%20would%20go%20on%20to%20support%20his%20political%20journey.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%202005%2C%20Vijayakanth%20founded%20the%20Desiya%20Murpokku%20Dravida%20Kazhagam%20(DMDK)%20in%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20political%20landscape%20dominated%20by%20the%20DMK%20and%20the%20AIADMK.%20The%20party's%20first%20electoral%20test%20in%20the%202006%20Assembly%20polls%20saw%20only%20Vijayakanth%20finish%20a%20winner.%20Despite%20the%20lone%20victory%2C%20DMDK%20did%20manage%20to%20cause%20a%20flutter%20in%20the%20state's%20politics.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%202011%20state%20polls%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20DMDK's%20best%20election.%20That%20year%2C%20Vijayakanth%20had%20forged%20an%20alliance%20with%20AIADMK%20and%20contest%2041%20seats.%20It%20managed%20to%20win%2029%20of%20them%2C%20more%20than%20the%20DMK's%20count.%20Vijayakanth%20became%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20and%20remained%20in%20the%20post%20till%202016.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20next%20election%20was%20a%20disappointment%20for%20Vijayakanth%20and%20DMDK.%20The%20senior%20leader%20lost%20the%20election%20and%20the%20deposit%20in%20the%202016%20election.%20His%20party%2C%20too%2C%20drew%20a%20blank.%20The%20DMDK%20failed%20to%20revive%20its%20fortunes%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20when%20it%20contested%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20AIADMK.%20Over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20Vijayakanth%20was%20ill%20and%20kept%20a%20low%20profile.%20His%20wife%20Premalatha%20had%20been%20handling%20the%20party's%20affairs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBesides%20his%20eventful%20careers%20as%20an%20actor%20and%20a%20politician%2C%20Vijayakanth%20also%20founded%20an%20engineering%20college%20and%20set%20up%20a%20television%20channel%20named%20