magazine%20back%20in%20the%2060s.%20She%20also%20made%20headlines%20for%20the%20swimsuit%20she%20wore%20in%20the%20film%20%3Ci%3EAn%20Evening%20In%20Paris%3C%2Fi%3E.%20%26quot%3BYour%20famous%20bikini%20shot...%20You%20know%20the%20shot%20I%20am%20talking%20about.%20Nobody%20else%20wanted%20it%20to%20happen.%20Even%20the%20photographer%20had%20some%20anxiety%20issues%20about%20doing%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Karan%20Johar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkoffee-with-karan-8-sharmila-tagore-on-being-told-about-saif-amrita-a-day-after-wedding-feeling-doubly-deprived-when-they-split-4755595%5C%22%3ESharmila%20Tagore%3C%2Fa%3E%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%20I%20do.%26quot%3B%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20in%20my%20boarding%20school%20used%20to%20ask%20me%2C%20is%20that%20your%20mum%3F%20I%20was%20very%20proud%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%20Sharmila%20Tagore%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20the%20photographer%20was%20slightly%20worried%20and%20I%20just%20thought%20I%20looked%20very%20nice.%20It%20really%20hurt%20me%20later%20because%20everybody%20interpreted%20it%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20I%20was%20upwardly%20mobile%2C%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20catch%20eyeballs.%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20that.%20When%20it%20came%20out%20in%20Filmfare%2C%20I%20was%20in%20London%20and%20I%20was%20unaware%20till%20Shakti%20(Samanta)%20ji%20called%20me%20and%20said%2C%20will%20you%20come%20back%20quickly%3F%20There%20are%20terrible%20things%20happening%20here.%20He%20said%20if%20you%20want%20to%20be%20in%20the%20public%20eye%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20way%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkwk-8-sharmila-tagore-shares-interesting-story-of-saif-skipping-university-to-go-out-with-this-person-4738753%5C%22%3ESharmila%20Tagore%3C%2Fa%3E%20mentioned%20that%20she%20sent%20a%20telegram%20to%20Tiger%20Pataudi.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20very%20upset%20with%20all%20this...%20Completely%20opposite%20of%20what%20I%20thought%20would%20happen%20so%2C%20I%20sent%20a%20telegram%20because%20those%20days%20you%20could%20send%20telegrams.%20So%2C%20I%20sent%20it%20to%20Tiger%20and%20he%20said%2C%20I%20am%20sure%20you%20are%20looking%20very%20nice.%20So%20that%20was%20my%20support.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20many%20ways%2C%20you%20perhaps%20experienced%20trolling%20also%20first.%20A%20version%20of%20trolling%2C%20of%20what%20happens%20on%20social%20media%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20joked%20Karan%20Johar.%20%26quot%3BTotally%2C%20I%20can't%20tell%20you...I%20believe%20questions%20were%20asked%20in%20the%20Parliament.%20It%20was%20not%20pleasant%20for%20me%20and%20learning%20I%20did.%20And%20after%20that%2C%20I%20was%20very%20careful%20and%20I%20chose%20%3Ci%3EAradhana%3C%2Fi%3E.%20It%20was%20%3Ci%3ERRR%3C%2Fi%3E%20of%20our%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharmila%20Tagore%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703741040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fhm76mv9_-sharmila_625x300_28_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkoffee-with-karan-8-sharmila-tagore-on-bikini-magazine-shoot-photographer-was-worried-i-thought-i-looked-very-nice-4756044%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt%20really%20hurt%20me%20later%20because%20everybody%20interpreted%20it%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20I%20was%20upwardly%20mobile%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharmila%20Tagore%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkoffee-with-karan-8-sharmila-tagore-on-bikini-magazine-shoot-photographer-was-worried-i-thought-i-looked-very-nice-4756044%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkoffee-with-karan-8-sharmila-tagore-on-bikini-magazine-shoot-photographer-was-worried-i-thought-i-looked-very-nice-4756044%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22http