age%20in%20physical%20acts%20with%20the%20tree.%20%26quot%3BA%20big%20misconception%20is%20that%20ecosexuality%20means%20sex%20between%20people%20and%20nature%2C%20it's%20a%20different%20way%20to%20explore%20the%20erotic.%20To%20watch%20the%20changing%20of%20the%20seasons%20is%20to%20me%20an%20erotic%20act.%20You%20go%20from%20death%20in%20winter%20and%20then%20everything%20comes%20alive%20in%20spring%20and%20mates.%20There%20are%20similarities%20between%20sex%20with%20people%20and%20the%20eroticism%20ecosexuals%20feel%20with%20nature%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ms%20Semyonova%2C%20ecosexuality%20%26quot%3Bis%20already%20present%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20people%26quot%3B%20and%20reconnecting%20with%20nature%20might%20help%20address%20many%20of%20the%20climate%20issues.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20reason%20we%20want%20to%20go%20for%20picnics%20in%20parks%20and%20hike%20in%20nature.%20What%20we%20fail%20to%20notice%20is%20that%20the%20reason%20we%20want%20this%20is%20to%20tap%20into%20the%20life%20force%20that%20comes%20from%20these%20things%2C%20which%20is%20the%20erotic.%20I%20believe%20that%20we%20could%20gain%20from%20having%20a%20more%20symbiotic%20relationship%20with%20nature%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703740560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fgrp2mpsg_ecosexual-woman_625x300_28_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fself-proclaimed-ecosexual-woman-says-she-is-in-love-with-oak-tree-4756007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20said%20that%20the%20romantic%20energy%20she%20feels%20with%20the%20tree%20is%20what%20she%20has%20always%20sought%20in%20a%20partner.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fself-proclaimed-ecosexual-woman-says-she-is-in-love-with-oak-tree-4756007%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%