moil%20happening%20worldwide%2C%20the%20relationship%20with%20our%20true%20friend%20in%20Asia%2C%20India%20has%20been%20progressing%20incrementally%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefinitely%2C%20we%20will%20be%20glad%20to%20see%20our%20dear%20friend%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20paying%20a%20visit%20to%20Russia%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20discuss%20all%20the%20relevant%2C%20current%20issues%20and%20talk%20to%20the%20prospects%20of%20the%20Russian%20and%20Indian%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20president%20asked%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20to%20convey%20his%20greetings%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20please%2C%20tell%20him%20that%20we%20want%20to%20see%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Putin%2C%20however%2C%20noted%20that%20India%20will%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bbusy%20political%20schedule%26quot%3B%20next%20year.%20%26quot%3BThe%20general%20elections%20in%20parliament%20are%20scheduled%20for%20next%20year.%20We%20wish%20our%20friends%20every%20success%20in%20that%20and%20we%20hope%20that...%20anyway%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20alignment%20of%20political%20forces%20would%20be%2C%20the%20traditional%20conventional%20friendly%20ties%20will%20persist%20between%20our%20nations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Russian%20President%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%2C%20India%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20resolution%20needs%20to%20be%20found%20through%20dialogue.%20New%20Delhi%20has%20spoken%20to%2C%20and%20met%2C%20Putin%20as%20well%20as%20Ukraine%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20and%20discussed%20the%20conflict.%20In%20his%20meeting%20with%20the%20Ukraine%20President%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%20India%20will%20do%20whatever%20it%20can%20to%20resolve%20the%20conflict.%20During%20a%20meeting%20with%20Putin%20in%20Samarkand%20in%202021%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20told%20him%20this%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20an%20era%20of%20war%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20also%20resisted%20pressure%20from%20the%20West%20to%20join%20the%20camp%20against%20Moscow.%20Despite%20global%20criticism%2C%20India%20continued%20to%20buy%20Russian%20oil%20after%20the%20West%20brought%20sanctions%20against%20Moscow%20for%20invading%20Ukraine.%20In%20an%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20had%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20told%20him%20to%20%26quot%3Bdo%20whatever%20is%20needed%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20build%20relations%20with%20the%20world.%20But%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20what%20benefits%20us%2C%20we%20should%20not%20back%20down.%20I%20should%20not%20expose%20our%20people%20to%20fuel%20inflation%20if%20I%20can%20find%20a%20way.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20said%2C%20'take%20a%20stand%20that%20benefits%20India'.%20We%20did%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20has%2C%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20questioned%20how%20Europe%20could%20prioritise%20its%20energy%20needs%20and%20expect%20India%20to%20act%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20country%2C%20he%20had%20said%2C%20was%20trying%20to%20get%20the%20best%20possible%20deal%20for%20its%20citizens%20and%20to%20cushion%20the%20impact%20of%20high%20energy%20prices%2C%20and%20India%20was%20no%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703737740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fo6km8rm8_modi-putin-getty_650x400_28_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvladimir-putin-s-jaishankar-wish-our-friends-every-success-and-hope-putin-on-lok-sabha-polls-4755680%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Referring%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20due%20next%20year%2C%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20wished%20%26quot%3Bfriends%20every%20success%26quot%3B%20and%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3Btraditional%20conventional%20friendly%