hat%20filled%20another%20tank.%20That%20meant%20either%20paying%20for%20that%20service%20or%20staying%20at%20RV%20parks%20and%20campgrounds%20with%20a%20dumping%20station%20included%20in%20the%20overnight%20price.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%247%20for%20freshwater%20might%20not%20seem%20like%20a%20huge%20cost%2C%20it%20could%20easily%20add%20up%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20of%20these%20hidden%20costs%20were%20small%20%E2%80%94%20and%20worth%20it.%20But%20if%20I%20decided%20to%20live%20in%20a%20van%20full%20time%2C%20they'd%20add%20up.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Business%20Insider's%20author%20in%20her%20rental%20van.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657c8bc350edbc52a864cf29%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20author%20in%20her%20rental%20van.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20%245%20here%20and%20there%20isn't%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20could%20easily%20see%20how%20these%20hidden%20costs%20could%20result%20in%20hundreds%20%E2%80%94%20if%20not%20thousands%20%E2%80%93%20of%20dollars%20if%20I%20took%20on%20the%20lifestyle%20full%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20there%20were%20plenty%20of%20hidden%20costs%20I%20didn't%20encounter.%20I've%20heard%20from%20plenty%20of%20other%20nomads%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-living-vans-rvs-share-advice-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20living%20in%20the%20vans%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20mechanical%20issues%20can%20rack%20up%20bills%2C%20insuring%20a%20van%20or%20RV%20can%20cost%20more%20than%20insurance%20for%20an%20average%20car%2C%20and%20Wi-Fi%20and%20internet%20plans%20aren't%20cheap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20two%3Cstrong%3E-%3C%2Fstrong%3Eweek%20trip%20uncovered%20plenty%20of%20hidden%20costs%2C%20but%20tha