20Nyay%20Yatra%20will%20cover%20Manipur%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20Assam%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Odisha%2C%C2%A0%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20yatra%20will%20not%20be%20completely%20conducted%20on%20foot%20like%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20was.%20Instead%2C%20it%20will%20involve%20bus%20travel%20with%20intermittent%20walking%20stretches.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20more%20details%20would%20be%20shared%20later%20with%20the%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%2C%20communication%2C%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20the%20Bharat%20Nyay%20Yatra%20will%20focus%20on%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20political%20justice%20of%20the%20country%2C%20just%20like%20how%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20had%20focussed%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eissues%20of%20economic%20disparities%2C%C2%A0%20polarisation%2C%20and%20dictatorship%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20president%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20will%20flag%20off%20the%20yatra%20from%20Imphal.%20Asked%20why%20Manipur%20was%20chosen%20as%20the%20state%20from%20where%20the%20East-West%20version%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20would%20begin%2C%20the%20Congress%20leaders%20said%20it%20was%20done%20to%20heal%20the%20wounds%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur.%20They%20added%20that%20it%20was%20also%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20important%20part%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20has%20witnessed%20some%20of%20the%20worst%20ethnic%20clashes%20for%20months%20which%20displaced%20thousands%20of%20people%20and%20left%20many%20dead.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20had%20also%20toured%20the%20state%20when%20the%20violence%20was%20going%20on.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20turned%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20visit%20the%20state%2C%20either%20during%20or%20after%20the%20clashes%2C%20into%20a%20significant%20political%20issue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsked%20if%20other%20partners%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20would%20also%20join%20the%20Bharat%20Nyaya%20Yatra%2C%20the%20party%20leaders%20said%20once%20again%20that%20the%20details%20were%20being%20worked%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20several%20leaders%20of%20other%20political%20parties%20had%20joined%20Gandhi%20for%20small%20stretches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20the%20election%20campaign%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20would%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20yatra%2C%20Vengugopal%20said%20the%20election%20campaign%20and%20the%20yatra%20can%20go%20on%20together%20and%20asked%20the%20media%20to%20wait%20for%20details.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703678923000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F24151138%2Fimage-746.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-leader-rahul-gandhi-to-start-bharat-nyay-yatra-on-january-14%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20yatra%2C%20which%20will%20cover%2085%20districts%20in%2014%20states%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20culminate%20on%20March%2020.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-leader-rahul-gandhi-to-start-bharat-nyay-yatra-on-january-14%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Babri%20Masjid%20Demolition%20to%20Ram%20Temple%20Inauguration%3A%20The%20Trajectory%20of%20Indian%20Politics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F27171854%2Fimage-1678.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20India%20gained%20independence%2C%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Findia-at-75-jawaharlal-nehru-tryst-with-destiny-full-text%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Tryst%20with%20Destiny%E2%80%99%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20future%20courses%20that%20India%20planned%20to%20undertake.%20He%20pledged%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20service%20of%20India%20means%20the%20service%20of%20the%20millions%20who%20suffer.%20It%20means%20the%20ending%20of%20poverty%2C%20ignorance%2C%20disease%2C%20and%20inequality%20of%20opportunity%E2%80%A6%20The%20ambition%20of%20the%20greatest%20man%20of%20our%20generation%20has%20been%20to%20wipe%20every%20tear%20from%20every%20eye.%20That%20may%20be%20beyond%20us%2C%20but%20as%20long%20as%20there%20are%20tears%20and%20suffering%2C%20our%20work%20will%20not%20be%20over.%E2%80%99%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Findia-at-75-jawaharlal-nehru-tryst-with-destiny-full-text%5C%22%3Earticulated%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20vision%20for%20the%20temples%20of%20modern%20India%20during%20the%20inauguration%20speech%20of%20the%20Bhakra%20Nangal%20dam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20archives%20describes%20it%20thus%3A%20%E2%80%9CWith%20great%20feeling%20the%20prime%20minister%20described%20these%20sites%20as%20%E2%80%9Ctemples%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fjawaharlal-nehru-inaugurates-bhakra-nangal-canal-system-symbolizing-india-s-progress-and-selfreliance-101688755029139.html%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fjawaharlal-nehru-inaugurates-bhakra-nangal-canal-system-symbolizing-india-s-progress-and-selfreliance-101688755029139.html%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1703740789321000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0yapkIgoP04Y-jw12-b_te%5C%22%3Eand%20places%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20worship%E2%80%9D%20where%20thousands%20of%20human%20beings%20were%20engaged%20in%20great%20constructive%20activity%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20millions%20of%20their%20fellow%20beings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20phrase%20%E2%80%98Temples%20of%20Modern%20India%E2%80%99%20served%20as%20the%20underlying%20theme%20for%20conceptualising%20public%20sectors%2C%20educational%20institutions%20promoting%20scientific%20temper%2C%20health%20facilities%2C%20and%20academies%20for%20the%20promotion%20of%20culture%2C%20among%20other%20aspects.%20The%20nearly%20four%20to%20five%20decades%E2%80%99%20journey%20with%20this%20undercurrent%20of%20%E2%80%98Modern%20Temples%E2%80%99%20took%20a%20significant%20turn%20in%20the%201980s.%20On%20one%20side%2C%20the%20response%20to%20the%20Shah%20Bano%20fiasco%20in%20dealing%20with%20minorities%20opened%20the%20floodgates%20of%20divisive%20politics%2C%20as%20communal%20forces%20unleashed%20a%20massive%20propaganda%20war%20against%20religious%20minorities.%20Simultaneously%2C%20the%20affirmative%20action%20for%20the%20downtrodden%2C%20with%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%2C%20gave%20impetus%20to%20temple%20politics%2C%20already%20a%20strategy%20in%20the%20playbook%20of%20Hindu%20nationalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20vision%20of%20%E2%80%98Temples%20of%20Modern%20India%2C%E2%80%99%20the%20quest%20for%20%E2%80%98temples%20underneath%20the%20mosque%E2%80%99%20brought%20to%20the%20fore%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20dispute.%20The%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20(RSS)%20progeny%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20came%20into%20existence%20in%201980%2C%20donning%20the%20cloak%20of%20%E2%80%98Gandhian%20Socialism%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20moderate%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20at%20the%20helm.%20Despite%20his%20moderate%20image%2C%20Vajpayee%20was%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20RSS%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20authored%20%3Cem%3EHindu%20Tan%20Man-Hindu%20Jeevan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Hindu%20soul%20and%20body-Hindu%20life)%2C%20and%20masked%20his%20Hindu%20nationalist%20politics.%20Vajpayee%20later%20made%20way%20for%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%2C%20who%20came%20up%20with%20the%20slogan%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Mandir%20Vahin%20Banayenge%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(We%20will%20build%20the%20temple%20where%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20is%20located).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20Combine%20was%20able%20to%20create%20a%20perception%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20was%20born%20precisely%20at%20the%20spot%20where%20the%20mosque%20was%20located.%20The%20Ram%20Rath%20Yatra%20gained%20momentum%20following%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20recommendations.%20However%2C%20this%20yatra%20left%20a%20trail%20of%20violence%20in%20its%20wake.%20Around%201990%2C%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20L.K.%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20Rath%20Yatra%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Flk-advani-rath-yatra-communal-violence-agra-babri-masjid-demolition%5C%22%3Enearly%201%2C800%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20India.%20The%20yatra%20was%20eventually%20halted%20when%20Lalu%20Yadav%20arrested%20Advani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20was%20demolished%20on%20December%206%2C%201992%2C%20by%20the%20karsevaks%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20had%20planned%20the%20demolition.%20During%20the%20event%2C%20leaders%20like%20Advani%2C%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%2C%20and%20Uma%20Bharati%20were%20seated%20on%20the%20stage%2C%20where%20slogans%20like%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CEk%20Dhakka%20Aur%20do%2C%20Babri%20Masjid%20Tod%20do%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Give%20one%20more%20push%2C%20break%20the%20Babri%20Mosque)%20and%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%9CYe%20to%20kevel%20Jhanki%20hai%20Kashi%20Mathura%20baki%20hai%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(this%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%2C%20Kashi%20Mathura%20will%20follow)%20were%20raised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20demolition%2C%20violence%20erupted%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Bhopal%2C%20Surat%2C%20and%20various%20other%20locations.%20In%20summary%2C%20the%20legal%20system%20bent%20over%20backwards%20to%20give%20the%20verdict%20of%20the%20case%20based%20on%20%E2%80%98faith%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20not%20giving%20any%20punishment%20to%20those%20who%20led%20the%20demolition.%20In%20its%20judgment%2C%20the%20judiciary%2C%20for%20better%20or%20worse%2C%20awarded%20the%20entire%20Babri%20Mosque%20land%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20glee%20of%20this%20%E2%80%98success%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20RSS%20combine%2C%20large%20funds%20were%20collected%20from%20home%20and%20abroad%20and%20now%2C%20a%20huge%20temple%20is%20ready%20to%20be%20inaugurated%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20himself%2C%20with%20all%20Hindu%20rituals.%20This%20will%20be%20a%20ceremony%20undertaken%20by%20the%20head%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98formally%20secular%E2%80%99%20state.%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20a%20regular%20election%20plank%20till%20it%20was%20demolished%20and%20after%20that%2C%20the%20building%20of%20the%20grand%20Ram%20temple%20was%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20election%20manifestos%20and%20electoral%20promises.%20The%20communal%20violence%20shot%20up%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%20along%20with%20the%20ghettoisation%20of%20Muslim%20community%2C%20the%20polarisation%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20electoral%20might%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsouthasianvoices.org%2Fauthor%2Famom%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsouthasianvoices.org%2Fauthor%2Famom%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1703740789321000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2gcJWVcw_npRIexgMGUzwa%5C%22%3EA.M.%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20research%20scholar%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Political%20Science%2C%20Manipur%20Central%20University%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20much%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20discourse%20has%20exacerbated%20communal%20tensions%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0Their%20actions%20have%20followed%20suit%2C%20with%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20in%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20and%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20in%202019%E2%80%A6%20By%20redefining%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsouthasianvoices.org%2Fthe-bjp-and-the-rise-of-communal-violence%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsouthasianvoices.org%2Fthe-bjp-and-the-rise-of-communal-violence%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1703740789321000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3xgSXWhChqOzvOV94mNZ0z%5C%22%3Eremanufacturing%3C%2Fa%3E%20Indian%20citizenship%20on%20the%20principles%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20broken%20the%20fate%20and%20legacy%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20secularism%20enshrined%20in%20its%20constitution.%E2%80%9D%20Now%20a%20ghettoised%20Muslim%20community%20has%20been%20pushed%20to%20the%20margins%20as%20second%20class%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20the%20temple%20is%20set%20to%20be%20inaugurated%2C%20efforts%20are%20underway%20to%20mobilise%20a%20large%20section%20of%20Hindus%20for%20this%20occasion.%20In%20countries%20like%20America%20and%20others%2C%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20NRIs%20are%20preparing%20for%20the%20event%20by%20organising%20various%20programmes.%20Back%20home%2C%20all%20the%20affiliates%20of%20the%20RSS%20have%20been%20activated%20to%20mobilise%20Hindus%20for%20the%20occasion%2C%20encouraging%20them%20to%20either%20visit%20the%20new%20temple%20or%20participate%20in%20rituals%20at%20local%20temples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20minor%20controversies%20about%20who%20has%20been%20invited%20and%20who%20has%20been%20left%20out.%20Advani%2C%20the%20chief%20architect%20of%20the%20demolition%20movement%2C%20and%20his%20close%20aide%20Joshi%20were%20initially%20advised%20by%20the%20temple%20trust%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20inauguration%20due%20to%20their%20old%20age%20and%20the%20biting%20cold%20in%20Ayodhya.%20On%20second%20thought%2C%20the%20VHP%2C%20the%20overarching%20organisation%2C%20has%20invited%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Babri%20demolition%20helped%20sectarian%20politics%20come%20to%20power%2C%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20temple%20seems%20to%20be%20yet%20another%20mechanism%20to%20consolidate%20polarisation%20and%20reap%20electoral%20dividends.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20special%20trains%20and%20buses%20are%20being%20planned%20for%20the%20occasion.%20Temple%20politics%20has%20reached%20its%20zenith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20time%20to%20recall%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98temples%20of%20Modern%20India%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20promotion%20of%20scientific%20temper.%20Currently%2C%20religiosity%20and%20blind%20faith%20are%20being%20heightened.%20As%20India%20started%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20colonial%20darkness%2C%20it%20also%20ensured%20a%20direction%20where%20the%20%E2%80%98last%20person%20in%20the%20line%E2%80%99%20was%20to%20be%20the%20primary%20focus.%20With%20the%20politics%20revolving%20around%20Ram%20Temple%2C%20to%20be%20followed%20by%20temples%20in%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%2C%20the%20deprivations%20of%20%E2%80%98last%20person%E2%80%99%20and%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Tryst%20with%20Destiny%E2%80%99%20promises%20have%20been%20dumped%20along%20with%20holding%20him%20responsible%20for%20all%20the%20ills%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fram-puniyani%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERam%20Puniyani%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20president%2C%20Centre%20of%20Study%20of%20Society%20and%20Secularism%20and%20has%20written%20several%20books%20including%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3ECommunal%20Politics%3A%20Facts%20Versus%20Myths%3Cem%3E%C2%A0(Sage%2C%202003)%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EDeconstructing%20Terrorist%20Violence%3Cem%3E%C2%A0(Sage%202015)%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EIndian%20Nationalism%20versus%20Hindu%20Nationalism%3Cem%3E%C2%A0(Pharos%202014)%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eand%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3ECaste%20and%20Communalism%3Cem%3E%C2%A0(Olive%202013).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703677956000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F27171854%2Fimage-1678.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffrom-babri-masjid-demolition-to-the-inauguration-of-ram-temple-the-trajectory-of-indian-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20Babri%20demolition%20helped%20sectarian%20politics%20come%20to%20power%2C%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20temple%20seems%20to%20be%20yet%20another%20mechanism%20to%20consolidate%20polarisation%20and%20reap%20electoral%20dividends.%20Temple%20politics%20has%20reached%20its%20zenith.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffrom-babri-masjid-demolition-to-the-inauguration-of-ram-temple-the-trajectory-of-indian-politics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Are%20We%20Headed%20for%20an%20Open%20Autocracy%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09092514%2FF-aWeDnboAA_Tym.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20in%20a%20time%20of%20momentous%20transition.%20Recent%20events%20suggest%20that%20as%20a%20nation%20we%20could%20be%20headed%20for%20life-altering%20turbulence.%20Separately%2C%20each%20episode%20is%20of%20high%20impact%2C%20and%20together%20they%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20accelerate%20a%20process%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20an%20open%20autocracy%20that%20could%20betoken%2C%20for%20all%20practical%20purposes%2C%20a%20one-party%20state%20apparatus%20%E2%80%93%20bidding%20adieu%20to%20the%20constitution%20we%20have%20nurtured%20for%2075%20years%20%E2%80%93%20if%20circumstances%20remain%20supportive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPredictably%20enough%2C%20in%20the%20short%20run%2C%20the%20most%20critical%20of%20these%20would%20be%20the%20return%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20office%20in%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20five%20months%20away.%20Whether%20as%20a%20propaganda%20trick%20or%20not%2C%20Modi%20has%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-to-become-third-largest-economy-in-my-third-term-guarantees-pm-modi%2Farticleshow%2F106064170.cms%5C%22%3Edeclared%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20third%20straight%20win%20for%20him%20was%20a%20foregone%20conclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20political%20map%2C%20it%20is%20a%20no-brainer%20that%20an%20effective%20coming%20together%20of%20the%20significant%20sections%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20major%20states%20will%20block%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20further%20advance%2C%20and%20that%20may%20result%20in%20his%20relegation%20to%20the%20background.%20He%20appears%20to%20have%20way%20too%20many%20adversaries%20within%20the%20saffron%20universe%20who%20could%20turn%20vengeful%20if%20power%20slips%20from%20his%20grasp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20shots%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20and%20not%20a%20few%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20the%20city%20of%20the%20RSS%20headquarters%2C%20or%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Bhopal%20and%20Jaipur%2C%20to%20say%20nothing%20of%20the%20second%20or%20third%20string%20players%20in%20elsewhere%2C%20who%20now%20pretend%20to%20be%20obsequious%20or%20dutiful%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20lose%20little%20time%20in%20getting%20even%20for%20real%20or%20perceived%20slights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20A%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20parties%20to%20recognise%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20historical%20moment%20they%20are%20navigating%20is%20poised%20to%20leave%20each%20of%20them%20isolated.%20Unity%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20an%20existential%20imperative.%20Are%20they%20aware%20of%20this%20reality%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-morning-after-15-takeaways-from-the-four-state-election-results%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520the%2520three%2520north%2520Indian%2CBharatiya%2520Janata%2520Party%2520since%25202019.%5C%22%3Erecent%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20northern%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20won%20decisively%2C%20showed%20that%20the%20local%20Congress%20satraps%20were%20blissfully%20unaware%20of%20the%20great%20political%20significance%20of%20these%20particular%20elections%20and%20carried%20on%20as%20though%20it%20was%20business%20as%20usual.%20So%20was%20the%20Congress%20leadership%2C%20else%20it%20would%20have%20rapped%20the%20three%20erring%20chieftains%20on%20their%20knuckles%20for%20their%20tunnel%20vision%20when%20there%20was%20still%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20was%20candid%20enough%20to%20bring%20up%20the%20subject%20in%20the%20December%2021%20meeting%20of%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20but%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20there%20is%20no%20knowing%20that%20the%20party%20won%E2%80%99t%20fluff%20its%20lines%20again%20when%20it%20deals%20with%20partners%20and%20allies%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20parliament%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20displaced%20from%20its%20high%20perch%2030-odd%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%93%20when%20the%20party%20was%20indeed%20a%20gargantuan%20enterprise%20%E2%80%93%20it%20has%20not%20quite%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20operate%20the%20philosophy%20of%20working%20in%20tandem%20with%20entities%20some%20of%20whom%20may%20well%20have%20a%20chip%20on%20their%20shoulder%2C%20being%20state%20parties%20that%20have%20made%20space%20for%20themselves%20by%20edging%20out%20the%20Congress%20over%20time.%20Working%20in%20genuine%20partnership%20with%20the%20Congress%20is%20a%20lesson%20that%20the%20state%20parties%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20also%20need%20to%20learn%20%E2%80%93%20and%20in%20quick%20time.%20There%20is%20not%20much%20time%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComparisons%20of%20the%20present%20situation%20with%20the%20Janata%20experiment%20do%20not%20hold%20water.%20The%20entity%20that%20regional%20parties%20of%20the%20day%20(including%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20precursor%2C%20Jana%20Sangh%2C%20was%20also%20just%20that%20at%20the%20time)%20were%20called%20upon%20to%20ally%20with%20was%20not%20the%20Congress%20but%20a%20disgruntled%20Congress%20rump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20played%20a%20high-stakes%20game%20in%20the%20recent%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%20He%20would%20have%20been%20acutely%20conscious%20that%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20serious%20setback%20in%20this%20battle%2C%20the%20wolves%20within%20the%20BJP%20would%20be%20out%2C%20baying%20for%20his%20blood.%20They%20would%20question%20his%20ability%20%E2%80%93%20or%20even%20credentials%20%E2%80%93%20to%20lead%20the%20party%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20These%20polls%20were%20close%20to%20being%20a%20point%20of%20reckoning%2C%20if%20not%20a%20make%20or%20break%20moment%2C%20for%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20although%20this%20was%20not%20apparent.%20Inherent%20in%20them%20was%20the%20potential%20to%20bring%20the%2010-year%20Modi%20rule%20to%20a%20turning%20point%2C%20whether%20history%20marked%20a%20turn%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20opponents%20figured%20any%20of%20this.%20They%20did%20not%20discern%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20moment.%20They%20went%20about%20as%20though%20this%20was%20just%20another%20poll%20battle.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20that%20a%20positive%20result%20would%20give%20Modi%20the%20leap%20and%20momentum%20in%20advance%20of%20the%20key%20election%20in%202024%20and%20help%20him%20set%20the%20field%20for%20the%20main%20battle%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Modi%20was%20taking%20his%20chances%2C%20he%20was%20not%20playing%20blind%20when%20he%20forced%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20key%20state%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20the%20architects%20of%20its%20past%20wins%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20%E2%80%93%20out%20of%20the%20reckoning%2C%20appealing%20to%20the%20electorate%20to%20cast%20their%20vote%20in%20his%20name.%20He%20was%20aware%20that%20the%20wind%20of%20communalism%20was%20in%20his%20sails.%20Two%20important%20considerations%20would%20have%20weighed%20as%20inordinately%20powerful%20factors%20%E2%80%93%20Ayodhya%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-leadership-shuffle-generational-change-strategy-for-modi-return%5C%22%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Leadership%20Shuffle%3A%20Generational%20Change%20or%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Strategy%20for%20a%20Return%20to%20Power%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20long%20four-year%20wait%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20decided%20to%20take%20up%20the%20Kashmir%20case%20%E2%80%93%20the%20challenge%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20jettisoning%20the%20constitutional%20autonomy%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%20The%20arguments%20being%20reported%20in%20the%20press%20gave%20ample%20indication%20which%20way%20things%20were%20going.%20To%20many%20it%20seemed%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20an%20event%20of%20such%20magnitude%20may%20not%20be%20unrelated%20to%20the%20electoral%20timetable.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffour-important-takeaways-from-the-supreme-court-ruling-on-jammu-and-kashmir%5C%22%3Ejudgment%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20on%20December%2011%2C%202023%2C%20after%20the%20recent%20assembly%20election%20results%20were%20announced%2C%20but%20forms%20a%20prelude%20to%20the%20parliament%20election%20due%20early%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArguably%20the%20most%20crucial%20event%20in%20setting%20the%20narrative%20of%20the%20new%20nationalism%20espoused%20by%20Modi%20and%20his%20party%20was%20the%20November%202019%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fayodhya-verdict-supreme-court-judgment%5C%22%3EAyodhya%20judgment%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Co