20in%20the%20mainstream%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20background%20became%20the%20setting%20for%20the%20win%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20which%20has%20unbound%20the%20Prometheus%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20who%20is%20portrayed%20as%20a%20heroic%20figure%20%E2%80%93%20greater%20than%20anything%20that%20has%20happened%20to%20the%20Hindu%20supremacist%20ideology%20since%20its%20inception.%20To%20add%20more%20grist%20to%20the%20mill%2C%20the%20temple%20disputes%20of%20Varanasi%20and%20Mathura%20appear%20to%20be%20continually%20stoked%20in%20the%20direction%20desired%20by%20the%20new%20nationalists%20by%20various%20levels%20of%20our%20judicial%20system%2C%20not%20excluding%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20BJP%20leaders%20now%20routinely%20refer%20to%20Modi%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98best%E2%80%99%20prime%20minister%20India%20has%20ever%20had%2C%20clearly%20surpassing%20Vajpayee%20and%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20great%20leaders%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement%2C%20such%20as%20Nehru%2C%20who%20is%20just%20about%20recognized%20as%20a%20former%20prime%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20and%20sought%20to%20be%20made%20less%20than%20significant.%20The%20already-established%20Modi%20cult%20owes%20not%20a%20little%20to%20its%20forceful%20promotion%20by%20Modi%20himself%2C%20who%20seeks%20to%20portray%20himself%20as%20larger%20than%20life%20and%20all-conquering.%20The%20G20%20meet%20in%20Delhi%20this%20year%20was%20an%20illustration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20the%20reign%20of%20this%20cult%20figure%20that%20a%20senior%20functionary%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20administration%20has%20declared%20the%20upcoming%20inaugural%20of%20the%20temple%20on%20January%2022%20as%20an%20event%20of%20history%20on%20par%20with%20the%20independence%20of%20India%20from%20British%20rule%20in%201947.%20The%20new%20chief%20minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20said%20that%20the%20prime%20meridian%2C%20the%20internationally%20recognised%20zero%20d