of%20three%20days%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2F141-here-are-all-the-mps-suspended-from-parliament-this-winter-session%5C%22%3Esuspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20nearly%20150%20opposition%20MPs%20because%20they%20made%20a%20ruckus%20and%20showed%20protest%20placards%20when%20their%20demand%20for%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20was%20ignored%20by%20the%20Chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20practical%20purposes%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20statement%20about%20not%20encountering%20a%20debate%20became%20a%20%3Cem%3Ediktat%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20those%20who%20run%20the%20chambers%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20plain%20that%20while%20Prometheus%20may%20have%20now%20broken%20free%2C%20thanks%20to%20multi-sided%20institutional%20capitulation%2C%20the%20institutions%20of%20modern%20India%20are%20themselves%20now%20in%20chains%2C%20waiting%20upon%20the%20will%20of%20the%20master.%20After%20this%2C%20if%20the%20next%20engagement%20is%20in%20the%20bag%20for%20the%20ruler%2C%20we%20may%20only%20anticipate%20a%20turn%20of%20enormous%20magnitude%20in%20our%20constitutional%20and%20political%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20inverted%20reality%20the%20INDIA%20opposition%20alliance%20can%20overlook%20at%20its%20own%20peril%20as%20it%20goes%20about%20in%20its%20inscrutable%20meandering%20fashion%20to%20chart%20out%20an%20electoral%20battle%20plan.%20Grand%20upsets%20are%20a%20part%20of%20history%2C%20including%20our%20own%20not%20so%20distant%20electoral%20past.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20chance%20that%20brings%20it%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fanand-k-sahay%5C%22%3EAnand%20K.%20Sahay%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20political%20commentator%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703673480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09092514%2FF-aWeDnboAA_Tym.jpeg%22%2C%22o