%3Cspan%3ENo%20details%20about%20the%20disengagement%20process%20or%20buffer%20zones%20have%20been%20shared%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20with%20the%20nation%20so%20far.%20The%20news%20of%20the%20landmark%20being%20dismantled%20was%20revealed%20for%20the%20first%20time%20by%20the%20elected%20councillor%20on%20Monday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20defence%20ministry%20and%20the%20army%20have%20not%20refuted%20the%20councillor%E2%80%99s%20statement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERezang%20La%20in%20Chushul%20sector%20saw%20a%20gallant%20battle%20fought%20till%20the%20%E2%80%9Clast%20man%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Clast%20round%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98C%E2%80%99%20company%20of%20the%2013%20Kumaon%20battalion%2C%20which%20was%20led%20by%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgainst%20all%20odds%20and%20grossly%20outnumbered%2C%20the%20valiant%20soldiers%20repulsed%20seven%20attacks%20by%20the%20Chinese%2C%20launched%20in%20waves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20heavy%20artillery%20shelling%20and%20fierce%20Chinese%20assaults%2C%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh%20and%20his%20113%20bravehearts%20delivered%20the%20heaviest%20blow%20to%20the%20Chinese.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gallantryawards.gov.in%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2Fhome_banner%2FBatleofrezangLa-2023-11-18.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edefence%20ministry%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20several%20hours%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20battle%20hung%20in%20%5Bthe%5D%20balance.%20Men%20were%20engaged%20in%20hand-to-hand%20combat.%20The%20Indian%20Company%20Commander%20even%20tried%20to%20launch%20a%20platoon%20counterattack%20to%20regain%20the%20height%2C%20Point%205300%20but%20did%20not%20succeed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20telephone%20line%20to%20the%20Battalion%20HQ%20was%20cut%20and%20the%20company%20radio%20set%20was%20destroyed%20in%20the%20initial%20stages.%20C%20Company%2013%20KUMAON%20was%20now%20on%20its%20own.%20No%20reinforcements%20could%20reach%20them.%20For%20them%20it%20was%20a%20fight%20to%20the%20finish.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20valour%20of%20the%20Charlie%20Company%20not%20only%20successfully%20stopped%20China%E2%80%99s%20advance%2C%20but%20it%20also%20resulted%20in%20the%20Chushul%20airport%20being%20saved%2C%20thereby%20preventing%20a%20possible%20Chinese%20occupation%20of%20the%20entire%20Ladakh%20region%20in%201962.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGeneral%20K.S.%20Thimayya%20was%20to%20state%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20rarely%20come%20across%20such%20%5Ban%5D%20example%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20world%20military%20history%20when%20braving%20such%20heavy%20odds%2C%20the%20men%20fought%20till%20the%20last%20bullet%20and%20the%20last%20man.%20Certainly%20the%20Battle%20of%20Rezang%20La%20is%20such%20a%20shining%20example.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20those%20at%20Rezang%20La%2C%20114%20soldiers%20perished%20in%20the%20fighting%20while%20five%20were%20captured%20by%20the%20Chinese.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20was%20posthumously%20awarded%20the%20Param%20Vir%20Chakra%20while%20another%20nine%20gallantry%20awards%20were%20won%20by%20the%20sub-unit%2C%20including%20five%20Vir%20Chakras%20and%20four%20Sena%20Medals.%20Singh%20was%20the%20second%20winner%20of%20the%20Param%20Vir%20Chakra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98C%E2%80%99%20Company%20was%20re-raised%20and%20rechristened%20as%20%E2%80%98Rezang%20La%20Company%E2%80%99%20in%201963.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gallantryawards.gov.in%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2Fstyles%2Fawardee_img%2Fpublic%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FVrC_Jem_RamChander_221202_SS_compressed-2023-03-23-1212-0303.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHonorary%20captain%20Ram%20Chander