ning-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egames%20and%20books%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20interactive%20and%20provide%20an%20opportunity%20to%20spend%20hours%20with%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalled%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20began%20the%20hunt%20for%20games%20and%20toys%20that%20not%20only%20helped%20him%20bond%20with%20his%20daughter%20but%20also%20contributed%20to%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F59319%2Fharsh-songra-my-child-app%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecognitive%20development%3C%2Fa%3E.%20During%20this%20search%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20not%20only%20are%20these%20toys%20and%20games%20hard%20to%20find%2C%20but%20they%20can%20also%20burn%20a%20hole%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20realisation%20was%20that%20it%20is%20very%20hard%20to%20make%20toys%20eco-friendly.%20There%20is%20some%20amount%20of%20plastic%20always%20present%20and%20it%20is%20harmful%20to%20the%20environment%20and%20the%20little%20ones%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20aspired%20to%20give%20his%20daughter%20the%20world%2C%20he%20also%20endeavoured%20to%20leave%20behind%20a%20cleaner%2C%20greener%2C%20and%20more%20sustainable%20world%20for%20her.%20Today%2C%20he%20owns%20The%20EleFant%20%E2%80%94%20a%20toy%20rental%20company%2C%20or%20in%20Sourabh%E2%80%99s%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98a%20labour%20of%20love%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20in%2014%20major%20cities%20in%20India%2C%20including%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Indore%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20etc.%20Curious%20about%20how%20the%20business%20works%20and%20how%20you%20can%20rent%20toys%20for%20your%20kids%3F%20Read%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESustainable%2C%20age-appropriate%20and%20fun%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20